grph.path

Class AbstractPath

  • java.lang.Object
    • grph.path.AbstractPath
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Path
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ArrayListPath, ArrayPath, PathExtender, SearchResultWrappedPath, SingletonPath

    public abstract class AbstractPath
extends java.lang.Object
implements Path
    A abstraction of path. A path is seen as a sequence of vertices. At this level, no implementation is defined.
